710783f-b.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 48th Street
710783f-b.text:
Twelfth Avenue, east side, south from West 49th to 48th
Street's, showing the old and the new frontage after
the widening of this Avenue. A swath of land was sliced
off of this side to provide for this marginal improvement.
Close observation will show several structures remaining.
September 26, 1928
May 21, 1936
P. L. Sperr

710782f.text:
